author: Patrick Cc:
description:
Pedro Pascal is Hollywood's newest favorite leading man.. But as studios race to cast him in everything, some are starting to question whether his rise is driven by talent… or because he is the perfect "product." This video dives into the hype, the backlash, and why Pedro Pascal might be the next star to fall victim to his own success.
